df['length_of_stay'] = (df['discharge_date'] - df['date_of_admission']).dt.days
df.groupby('medical_condition')['length_of_stay'].mean().sort_values(ascending=False).head(10).plot(kind='bar', figsize=(10,5))
plt.title('Top 10 Medical Conditions by Average Length of Stay')
plt.ylabel('Average Days')
plt.xticks(rotation=45)
plt.show()
